Value FAN_TRAY (\S+\s+\d+)
Value STATE (\S+)
Value SPEED (\d+%)
Value AIRFLOW (\S+-to-\S+)
Value POWER (\d+W)
Value RPM (\d+)

Start

  ^\s*State:\s*(${STATE})

  ^\s*RPM:\s*(${RPM})
